replies.body:
Your argument of "if you can't handle it, just stop playing" is a double-edged sword. Just the same as you can use it to tell people that they shouldn't play League if they can't handle flame or asshole-ish behavior, so too can I tell you this;

If you don't want to get punished and eventually banned, stop breaking the rules. If you can't handle Riot's criticisms on your behavior, then maybe you shouldn't be misbehaving in their game. If you play anything competitive and start turning on your teammates, you're not going to get a "yeah it's cool you just got competitive spirit" - you're going to get punished. Don't like it? Don't play.

Also, nice non-sequitur with the skins comment.
